WEBVTT

17:55.024 --> 17:56.066
Offer? Offer?

17:56.066 --> 17:57.524
Err... Do you have
a figure in mind?

17:57.566 --> 17:58.566
Errr...

17:58.566 --> 17:59.608
No. You tell.

17:59.608 --> 18:01.191
Are you okay with profit sharing?

18:01.191 --> 18:02.191
Oh!

18:02.941 --> 18:04.274
Sir... No...
